sentences: Hildreth was born on July 13, 1928, in Memphis, Texas.
In the 1960s, she hosted Wills Family Inspirational Time.
She was inducted into the Gospel Music Hall of Fame in 2005, and the Southern Gospel Museum and Hall of Fame in 2007.

sentences: Lou Wills Hildreth (July 13, 1928 – February 28, 2019) was an American Southern gospel performer, songwriter, talent agent and television host.
Hildreth was married to Howard Hildreth for 72 years.
Lou died two months and two days after her husband.
